{"tid":2377061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[手足?] 中年漢被拒入封鎖範圍回家　激動揮拳襲警　警面腫送院","createTime":"2021-01-23T09:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T15:26:10.000Z","uid":224066,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3889cc252a242cb9533d665416c0672d94507b10","tid":2377061,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210123/429608179651973120542390.jpeg/dt2Ob3H4GcO0FAco5pqfqCrWhfC9ik_SNWhxAjVocQI?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210123%2F429608179651973120542390.jpeg%2Fdt2Ob3H4GcO0FAco5pqfqCrWhfC9ik_SNWhxAjVocQI%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=c68d6c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情肆虐，政府於今日（23日）凌晨4時宣布，封鎖佐敦一帶的指定區域，並進行對區內所有人士強制檢測，其間所有人不得離開處所。今日（23日）早上9時許，一名47歲姓謝男子走至上海街及南京街交界。他報稱為上址居民，打算回家時被警員制止，有警員向他解釋其住所位於封鎖範圍內，因此無法進入。<br />\n<br />\n該名身穿綠色外套及持藍色環保袋的謝男，聽罷警員解釋後情緒激動，揮拳襲擊其中一名男警員。謝男當場被按地制服、鎖上手銬，他涉嫌襲警被捕；遇襲的男警面部被打腫，獲送院治理。據悉，由於謝男為佐敦指定範圍的居民，所以防疫人員先將他帶回家檢疫，待檢測結果為陰性後，屆時警方會作拘捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210123/429608177084928000897632.jpeg/ZxVOCyMhmzKm2UCZ6wVPc_e_Mh6oJ4BPGo1MECCNTBA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210123%2F429608177084928000897632.jpeg%2FZxVOCyMhmzKm2UCZ6wVPc_e_Mh6oJ4BPGo1MECCNTBA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=124fd308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210123/429604835638120448426583.jpeg/hZ5Mov3pPcoIwScI9X34OUk1_ab42Gw6WgzO7GAMzuw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210123%2F429604835638120448426583.jpeg%2FhZ5Mov3pPcoIwScI9X34OUk1_ab42Gw6WgzO7GAMzuw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dc54d7a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c45f0c5082be86d7c7765e3ef0771d51dcfd99c4","tid":2377061,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0